<subSubSection lastPageId="213" lastPageNumber="214" pageId="212" pageNumber="213" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="212.[125,654,1499,1757]" box="[154,361,1616,1639]" pageId="212" pageNumber="213">MALE: Unknown.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="212.[125,654,1499,1757]" lastBlockId="212.[701,1230,1499,1756]" pageId="212" pageNumber="213">
FEMALE: Judging from Mello-Leitão’s (1916) original description, this spider is probably similar to most southeast-Brazilian representatives of 
<taxonomicName box="[344,491,1734,1757]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Mesabolivar" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="212" pageNumber="213" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
